            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an epitaxy method for reducing the surface roughness of a silicon carbide homoepitaxial wafer, and the method comprises the steps: placing a silicon carbide substrate at a groove of a graphite tray, and placing the graphite tray on a graphite pedestal of a reaction cavity; the reaction cavity is filled and pumped for multiple times through inert gas, and after emptying is completed, the main hydrogen amount is set to be 10-40 slm, and the cavity pressure is set to be 50 mbar to 100 mbar; raising the temperature in the reaction cavity to a first preset temperature of 1450-1550 DEG C, controlling the tray to rotate at 0.6-1.5 s/r, and annealing in the in-situ furnace for 5-10 minutes; then continuously heating to a second preset temperature of 1550-1750 DEG C, simultaneously increasing the hydrogen flow to 80-120slm, and when the temperature is increased to the second preset temperature, cooperating with a flow carbon source/silicon source, and maintaining the etching time for 5-30min; after the etching is finished, introducing a carbon source and a silicon source to grow a buffer layer with a low C/Si ratio for 2-10 minutes by utilizing an epitaxial growth process; after the buffer layer is finished, secondary etching is carried out, and the etching time is maintained for 0-5 min; after the etching is finished, keeping a proper C/Si ratio to grow for 0-5 minutes; and then changing the source quantity of the carbon source silicon until the growth of an epitaxial layer with a relatively high carbon-silicon ratio is realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种降低碳化硅同质外延片表面粗糙度的外延方法，步骤包括：将碳化硅衬底放在石墨托盘凹槽处，将石墨托盘放入反应腔的石墨基座上；利用惰性气体对反应腔内进行多次充抽，排空完毕后，设定主氢气量为10‑40slm，腔体压力50mbar‑100mbar；将反应腔体内的温度升温到第一预设温度1450‑1550℃，并且控制托盘旋转维持0.6‑1.5s/r，原位炉内退火5‑10min；随后继续升温到第二预设温度1550‑1750℃，同时增加氢气流量至80‑120slm，升到第二预设温度时，配合流量碳源/硅源，维持刻蚀时间5‑30min；刻蚀结束后，利用外延生长工艺，通入碳源和硅源进行C/Si比较低的缓冲层生长2‑10min；缓冲层结束后，进行二次刻蚀，刻蚀时间维持0‑5min；刻蚀结束后，保持合适C/Si比生长0‑5min；继而更改碳源硅源源量至转为较高碳硅比的外延层生长。"
                }
            ]
